AUDIENCE: Hey, there, guys.

00:36:37.840 --> 00:36:38.810
Thanks for coming.

00:36:38.810 --> 00:36:39.870
So a two-part question.

00:36:39.870 --> 00:36:41.710
One is what's the
order of magnitude

00:36:41.710 --> 00:36:44.510
of the number of stoves that
