And if so, what's its capacity?

00:43:05.280 --> 00:43:08.930
What is the total power
output to the USB port?

00:43:08.930 --> 00:43:10.290
Some other stuff like that?

00:43:10.290 --> 00:43:11.550
RYAN GIST: Sure.

