So currently, there is
no battery in the stove.

00:43:14.360 --> 00:43:16.180
That adds cost,
again, to the product.

00:43:16.180 --> 00:43:18.930
And so until we can bring
the rest of the cost down,

00:43:18.930 --> 00:43:20.560
we're going to leave
the battery out.

00:43:20.560 --> 00:43:24.380
We are working both in our
outdoor recreation markets

00:43:24.380 --> 00:43:27.700
and in our emerging markets
on some lighting options that

00:43:27.700 --> 00:43:29.700
can utilize the USB
power from the stove

00:43:29.700 --> 00:43:32.570
to provide light, but also
have a battery on that side

00:43:32.570 --> 00:43:34.535
of the system to store things.

